Many files use `ctx.scopedRepo.hypercerts.*` and `ctx.scopedRepo.records.*` ŌĆö these will break at the type level. That's expected. They will be migrated in Phase 2-4 to use `ctx.agent.com.atproto.repo.*` with `ctx.targetDid`.

